  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda  \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dad\u0db8 Hyper Casual \u2013 eSports Championship  \u0d85\u0daf \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka's biggest Hyper Casual \u2013 eSports Championship starts today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka's first and biggest Hyper Casual - eSports tournament, organized by the Ministry of Youth and Sports, IMI Games and SLT Mobitel, will start today (15) at 5 pm.",
        "The main objective of this tournament is to hone the skills of Sri Lankan cyber athletes and provide the necessary technical background and contribution to create cyber games.",
        "SLT Mobitel has come forward to provide all gifts and data to over 300 athletes who win the tournament.",
        "This Hyper Casual \u2013 eSports tournament held at the national level will be held for 02 days from today and the sportswomen will have to advance in this tournament through 06 games.",
        "All sportswomen who progress through the 06 related sports challenges will finally have the opportunity to reach the national scoreboard, where the player who scores the most points will be able to inherit the national championship.",
        "IMI Games, which introduced the Hyper Casual game to Sri Lanka, will perform all the technical and organizational work of this tournament and this will give Sri Lankan cyber sports players a new experience at the national level."
      ],
